      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; existing published experimental dataset is sufficient for validation at this risk level.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, generation of new experimental data specifically for this assessment is not required. The Morrison et al. (2019) dataset provides adequate coverage of the operating envelope with n=3 replicate measurements per operating point, sufficient for the validation comparison at this model risk level."
